{"tid":1977421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聖保羅生冀讀法律守護香港","createTime":"2020-04-18T03:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T03:28:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"8b3b547f144f0aa1aee3bed0ef808d9c6acf440d","tid":1977421,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:19:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200418/NKENBDM7DVNWLK5SGUWP6YHVLI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200418%2FNKENBDM7DVNWLK5SGUWP6YHVLI%2F&d=0xR7vGHOl893LUq1yoppesjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=c2c2aff6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200418%2FNKENBDM7DVNWLK5SGUWP6YHVLI%2F&h=23b0dd25\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200418/NKENBDM7DVNWLK5SGUWP6YHVLI/</a><br />\n<br />\n聖保羅生冀讀法律守護香港<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】從抗爭到抗疫，從停課到文憑試一再延期，應屆中六生經歷了最動盪的一年。Desmond是傳統名校聖保羅書院的中六生，也是該校反修例關注組召集人，經過這大半年的衝擊，立志要考入法律系守護香港核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n2019年6月12日是聖保羅書院中五級應考期終試數學科的日子，開考前Desmond聯同同學們，不是捧讀筆記為考試最後衝刺，而是盯着手機觀看直播金鐘的最新情況。「我嚟到世上18年，6.12時見到的畫面，係我從冇想像過會發生喺香港呢個屋企。」Desmond更無法想像，香港警察會向中信大廈門外人群射催淚彈，「根本就係意圖謀殺」。<br />\n<br />\n升中六的暑假，對很多學生來說都是密集式補課和溫習的時間，但Desmond整個暑假「碌手機新聞時間多過讀書好多」，製作文宣出聲明更佔不少時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200418/large/1587140106_3274.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200418%2Flarge%2F1587140106_3274.jpg&h=5d28d580&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDesmond立志考入法律系以捍衞香港核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「冇反修例唔會成長咁多」<br />\n<br />\n他是聖保羅書院反修例關注組成員，開學後多次籌備罷課和在學校唱《願榮光歸香港》，「扑咪」接受傳媒訪問，亦不時到示威遊行現場拍照，為時代留紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n「入到大學，讀到你想讀嘅科，先有專業知識同資格救香港！」去年11月一位長輩提醒，令Desmond決定暫時抽身，專心應付文憑試。看到很多警暴場面，警察不受法律制裁，不幸被捕的手足卻被重判，令他決心要考進法律系，希望更了解香港的法制，尋找改變的機會，阻止社會繼續崩壞下去。<br />\n<br />\n不料，香港又遇上世紀疫症，Desmond的模擬試只考到一半便告停課，只能在網上完成模擬試。他指反修例運動會是這代人最深刻、最不能磨滅的事，經歷過後，想法更正面：「如果冇反修例事件，可能好多人又唔會成長咁多。」<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄧力行"},{"pid":"7a7045669442dbf70a400cf4fa7dd8d22fd44e28","tid":1977421,"uid":194326,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"挖返dead body鞭"},{"pid":"9c390837620cecb2dc5f013fc91dd26a4b1260fc","tid":1977421,"uid":35457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"呢一年大家都成長左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f078d331e7fa491f0e0770240ee5c70be83b6398","tid":1977421,"uid":304141,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"544ec477a41503c8c5108212901106fc5f0a128d","tid":1977421,"uid":14090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:22:22.000Z","msg":"Dead body 2.0?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52e0fabdbbb97ee28226491ed0dad87f39bc8f2f","tid":1977421,"uid":224479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f078d331e7fa491f0e0770240ee5c70be83b6398","tid":1977421,"uid":304141,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:21:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:24:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d74419fa3a77e21231649f8c308bffae8adcede0","tid":1977421,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:25:48.000Z","msg":"楊岳橋接班人"},{"pid":"931e8d390f14cfd4fa993b8b686e9796c324f7fe","tid":1977421,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c390837620cecb2dc5f013fc91dd26a4b1260fc","tid":1977421,"uid":35457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"呢一年大家都成長左好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:26:02.000Z","msg":"依個真，對好多事物既睇法都唔同咗"},{"pid":"9aab45dacdcbbf4b3aa19ee185eee75f2045da88","tid":1977421,"uid":46161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:26:51.000Z","msg":"多個律師幫示威者都好！ 冇必要對佢咁苛刻，青年諗野一定係會理想化左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />支持佢，比心機！"},{"pid":"5fc48897aa327992e45fffd1fe063c90cc72a07d","tid":1977421,"uid":318069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T03:28:10.000Z","msg":"over my dead body!"}]}